  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK501">
<l>aṟamporu ḷiṉpa muyiracca nāṉkiṉ</l>
<l> ṟiṟanterintu tēṟap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a minister) be chosen, after he has been tried by means of these four things, viz,-his virtue, (love of) money, (love of) sexual pleasure, and tear of (losing) life.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
